t helpers per plan.md interfaces.\n\n---\n\n### CRIT-003: Missing US-3 E2E Integration Test\n\n**File**: `tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js`\n**Requirement**: AC-3.1, AC-3.2, AC-3.3, AC-3.4\n\n**Issue**: The E2E test file for the main chain (start вЖТ status вЖТ stop) does not exist.\n\n**Spec Requirements**:\n- AC-3.1: Test start вЖТ status вЖТ stop main chain\n- AC-3.2: Verify state transitions: idle вЖТ running вЖТ stopped\n- AC-3.3: Verify error handling: duplicate start, empty stop\n- AC-3.4: Test run time < 30s\n\n**Impact**: Core user story US-3 has zero test coverage.\n\n---\n\n## HIGH Findings (3)\n\n### HIGH-001: Missing US-4 Integration Test\n\n**File**: `tests/integration/plan-version-flow.test.js`\n**Requirement**: AC-4.4, T-137\n\n**Issue**: Integration test for plan file version flow doesn't exist.\n\n**Spec Requirements**:\n- Dynamic plan switch during pipeline\n- Version upload вЖТ activate flow\n\n---\n\n### HIGH-002: Missing Error Path Tests\n\n**File**: `tests/services/error-paths.test.js`\n**Requirement**: T-114\n\n**Issue**: Dedicated error path tests for control layer not created.\n\n**Spec Requirements**: AC-2.4 вАФ All error paths have corresponding test cases.\n\n---\n\n### HIGH-003: Task Tracking Inconsistency\n\n**Files**: \n- `tests/fixtures/plans/` вАФ Exists with valid fixtures\n- `tests/fixtures/states/` вАФ Exists with state fixtures\n\n**Issue**: Test fixtures exist but T-001, T-002, T-003, T-004 are marked incomplete. This indicates:\n1. Either tasks were completed but not updated\n2. Or fixtures were created outside F-007 scope\n\n**Recommendation**: Verify fixture provenance and update task tracking.\n\n---\n\n## MEDIUM Findings (2)\n\n### MED-001: Test Runner Warning\n\n**Issue**: Running `node --test tests/**/*.test.js` produces warning:\n```\n(node:...) Warning: node:test run() is being called recursively within a test file. skipping running files.\n```\n\n**Root Cause**: This appears to be related to how the glob patte