izm\n  78вЖТ\n  79вЖТ---\n  80вЖТ\n  81вЖТ## Task Details\n  82вЖТ\n  83вЖТ### T-001: Create test fixtures directory structure\n  84вЖТ- **Goal**: Establish standardized fixture organization\n  85вЖТ- **Input**: None\n  86вЖТ- **Output**: `tests/fixtures/`, `tests/fixtures/plans/`, `tests/fixtures/states/`\n  87вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Directories exist, .gitkeep in each\n  88вЖТ- **Complexity**: Low\n  89вЖТ\n  90вЖТ### T-005: Create fixture loader helper\n  91вЖТ- **Goal**: Provide lazy-loading utility for test fixtures\n  92вЖТ- **Input**: Fixture relative path\n  93вЖТ- **Output**: File content (string or parsed JSON)\n  94вЖТ- **Acceptance**: `loadFixture()`, `loadJsonFixture()`, `getFixturePath()` exported\n  95вЖТ- **Complexity**: Low\n  96вЖТ\n  97вЖТ### T-006: Create mock runner helper\n  98вЖТ- **Goal**: Replace real shell execution with controlled responses\n  99вЖТ- **Input**: Response map configuration\n 100вЖТ- **Output**: Mock runner function compatible with pipeline-control-service\n 101вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Supports action routing, response sequencing, delay simulation\n 102вЖТ- **Complexity**: Medium\n 103вЖТ\n 104вЖТ### T-007: Create mock Telegram context helper\n 105вЖТ- **Goal**: Simulate Telegraf bot context for handler tests\n 106вЖТ- **Input**: Context overrides (message, user, chat)\n 107вЖТ- **Output**: Mock context object with reply methods\n 108вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Compatible with command handlers, supports document upload\n 109вЖТ- **Complexity**: Medium\n 110вЖТ\n 111вЖТ### T-121: Create E2E test: start вЖТ status вЖТ stop main chain\n 112вЖТ- **Goal**: Verify primary user flow works end-to-end\n 113вЖТ- **Input**: Mock runner with state transitions\n 114вЖТ- **Output**: Test file with passing assertions\n 115вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Tests idleвЖТrunningвЖТstoppedвЖТidle cycle, validates responses\n 116вЖТ- **Complexity**: High\n 117вЖТ\n 118вЖТ### T-134: Add version management tests: upload, list, switch\n 119вЖТ- **Goal**: Verify plan file version operations\n 120вЖТ- **Input**: Temp directory, sample plan files\n 121вЖТ- **Output**: Test cases for upload, list, switch operations\n 122вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Covers success and failure paths, isolates file system\n 123вЖТ- **Complexity**: Medium\n 124вЖТ\n 125вЖТ### T-141: Enhance permission tests: admin/operator/viewer boundaries\n 126вЖТ- **Goal**: Verify permission level enforcement\n 127вЖТ- **Input**: Mock users with different permission levels\n 128вЖТ- **Output**: Test cases for each level\n 129вЖТ- **Acceptance**: Tests command access per level, verifies rejection messages\n 130вЖТ- **Complexity**: Medium\n 131вЖТ\n 132вЖТ---\n 133вЖТ\n 134вЖТ## Parallelization Guide\n 135вЖТ\n 136вЖТ**Can run in parallel** (marked with [P]):\n 137вЖТ- T-001, T-002, T-003, T-004 (fixtures setup)\n 138вЖТ- T-006, T-007 (mock helpers)\n 139вЖТ- T-101 ~ T-104 (US-1 tests)\n 140вЖТ- T-111 ~ T-114 (US-2 tests)\n 141вЖТ- T-131 ~ T-133 (US-4 validation tests)\n 142вЖТ- T-141 ~ T-146 (US-5 permission tests)\n 143вЖТ\n 144вЖТ**Must run sequentially**:\n 145вЖТ- T-005 depends on T-001 ~ T-004\n 146вЖТ- T-121 ~ T-124 (E2E tests need mock runner ready)\n 147вЖТ- T-137 (integration test needs other tests stable)\n 148вЖТ- T-901 ~ T-903 (polish phase)\n 149вЖТ"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeb77959cce91c4c30f48375af46","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:05:51.970Z","_requestId":"1b6b97b85f114aa389b904b402a47efc"}
