izm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm` and `.prizm-docs/pipeline/scripts.prizm`\n  29вЖТ\n  30вЖТ### Acceptance Criteria Met\n  31вЖТ\n  32вЖТ- US-1: Unified config loading with readable validation errors\n  33вЖТ- US-2: Standard directory structure with Python/JS parity\n  34вЖТ- US-3: Unified script execution API (run/status/stop/logs/retry/reset)\n  35вЖТ- US-4: TypeScript and ESLint baseline established\n  36вЖТ\n  37вЖТ### Verification\n  38вЖТ\n  39вЖТ- `npm run typecheck`: 0 errors\n  40вЖТ- `npm run lint`: 0 warnings\n  41вЖТ- `npm test`: 29 tests pass\n  42вЖТ\n  43вЖТ---\n  44вЖТ\n  45вЖТ## F-002: Telegram Pipeline Command Router\n  46вЖТ\n  47вЖТ**Status:** completed  \n  48вЖТ**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n  49вЖТ\n  50вЖТ### Deliverables\n  51вЖТ\n  52вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/index.js` - Router entry point (auth, parse, validate, dispatch)\n  53вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/parser.js` - Command parsing with alias support\n  54вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/registry.js` - Dynamic command registration\n  55вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/validator.js` - Parameter validation\n  56вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/formatter.js` - User-friendly error messages\n  57вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/help.js` - Dynamic help text generation\n  58вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` - Pipeline command handler\n  59вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/bugfix.js` - Bugfix shortcut handler\n  60вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/planner.js` - Planner pipeline handler\n  61вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js` - Status query handler\n  62вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js` - Logs query handler\n  63вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Stop pipeline handler\n  64вЖТ- Unit tests in `tests/bot/commands/`\n  65вЖТ- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f002-command-router.integration.test.js`\n  66вЖТ- Documentation in `.prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm`\n  67вЖТ\n  68вЖТ### Acceptance Criteria Met\n  69вЖТ\n  70вЖТ- US-1: Pipeline command with run/status/logs/stop subcommands\n  71вЖТ- US-2: Bugfix co