r/viewer) with env config\n 273вЖТ- `src/security/param-sanitizer.js` - Parameter sanitization with path traversal and shell injection protection\n 274вЖТ- `src/security/confirmation-manager.js` - Text-based confirmation flow with 60s timeout\n 275вЖТ- `src/security/guard.js` - Unified guard middleware for command handlers\n 276вЖТ- `src/security/system-guard.js` - System exec command guard with ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC control\n 277вЖТ- `src/security/index.js` - Module exports\n 278вЖТ- `src/services/audit-log-service.js` - JSON Lines audit logging with rotation (10MB/5 files)\n 279вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/audit.js` - /audit command for log query (admin-only)\n 280вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` - Updated with force-unlock, confirmation flow, audit logging\n 281вЖТ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Updated with confirmation flow\n 282вЖТ- `src/config.js` - Extended with security configuration\n 283вЖТ- `.env.example` - Updated with USER_PERMISSIONS, AUDIT_LOG_* vars\n 284вЖТ- Unit tests in `tests/security/`\n 285вЖТ- Unit tests in `tests/services/audit-log-service.test.js`\n 286вЖТ- Integration tests in `tests/integration/security-flow.test.js`, `tests/integration/security-extended.test.js`\n 287вЖТ- Documentation in `.prizm-docs/runtime/security.prizm`\n 288вЖТ\n 289вЖТ### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 290вЖТ\n 291вЖТ- US-1: User Permission Levels - Three-tier model (admin/operator/viewer) with USER_PERMISSIONS env config\n 292вЖТ- US-2: High-Risk Command Authorization - stop/reset/force-unlock require admin, retry requires operator\n 293вЖТ- US-3: Parameter Sanitization - Path traversal, shell injection, and dangerous character protection\n 294вЖТ- US-4: Confirmation for Sensitive Actions - Text-based CONFIRM with 60s timeout, --force for admin\n 295вЖТ- US-5: Audit Logging - JSON Lines format with rotation, query by user/time/action\n 296вЖТ\n 297вЖТ### High-Risk Command Matrix\n 298вЖТ\n 299вЖТ| Command | Min Permission | Confirmation |\n 300вЖТ|